1
00:00:09,030 --> 00:00:10,260
Shen Zhengran committed treason,

2
00:00:10,260 --> 00:00:11,260
was thrown into death row,

3
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:13,360
and his wife and children were enslaved.

4
00:00:13,360 --> 00:00:14,660
My daughter is kind-hearted

5
00:00:14,660 --> 00:00:16,320
and bought her former friend.

6
00:00:16,830 --> 00:00:19,260
Who knew this woman, just like her father,

7
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:20,530
is completely vicious,

8
00:00:20,530 --> 00:00:22,300
and stole my daughter's husband.

9
00:00:22,300 --> 00:00:23,100
Your Majesty,

10
00:00:23,130 --> 00:00:26,330
such a venomous woman will ruin General Weibei.

11
00:00:27,860 --> 00:00:29,330
So that's how it is.

12
00:00:29,330 --> 00:00:30,730
In that case...

13
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:34,930
You knew her identity,

14
00:00:34,930 --> 00:00:36,700
yet you sent her to sleep with me for three days.

15
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:38,330
You deliberately made me obsessed with her and fall in love with her,

16
00:00:38,330 --> 00:00:39,930
you scheming old dog!

17
00:00:45,460 --> 00:00:46,530
Stop it.

18
00:00:53,130 --> 00:00:54,160
Lu Jingxing,

19
00:00:54,160 --> 00:00:56,360
who are you showing this barbaric behavior to?

20
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:57,830
To Your Majesty, of course.

21
00:00:57,830 --> 00:00:59,290
So that Your Majesty knows

22
00:00:59,330 --> 00:01:01,530
I have fallen deeply into Grand Tutor Wei's honey trap.

23
00:01:01,530 --> 00:01:03,800
Now, no one can separate Shen Lvyi and me.

24
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,430
Not even me?

25
00:01:06,330 --> 00:01:07,130
Your Majesty.

26
00:01:07,700 --> 00:01:09,430
My father betrayed your grace.

27
00:01:09,700 --> 00:01:11,360
As the daughter of a criminal,

28
00:01:11,530 --> 00:01:14,330
I dare not cause any more trouble because of myself.

29
00:01:14,330 --> 00:01:16,130
I beg Your Majesty to withdraw the order.

30
00:01:16,130 --> 00:01:19,530
I am willing to return to the Grand Tutor's manor and work until death.

31
00:01:19,530 --> 00:01:21,330
Truly the eldest daughter of the Shen family.

32
00:01:21,330 --> 00:01:22,260
Appropriate in words and deeds,

33
00:01:22,260 --> 00:01:23,530
retreating to advance.

34
00:01:23,530 --> 00:01:25,500
Shen Zhengran was unyielding,

35
00:01:25,530 --> 00:01:28,560
and the daughter he taught is also extraordinary.

36
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:29,500
Humph.

37
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:31,830
I am the Emperor.

38
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:33,030
My words are gold,

39
00:01:33,030 --> 00:01:34,430
and cannot be taken back.

40
00:01:34,430 --> 00:01:37,360
How can I go back on my word because of a lowly slave like you,

41
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:40,560
and hurt the bond between the Emperor and General Weibei?

42
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:41,630
Your Majesty is wise.

43
00:01:41,630 --> 00:01:42,660
Stop flattering.

44
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,229
Your Majesty,

45
00:01:44,229 --> 00:01:45,700
stop nagging.

46
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:47,660
Getting to the bottom of this,

47
00:01:47,660 --> 00:01:49,560
since you knew Shen Lvyi's identity back then,

48
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:51,530
why did you send her to General Weibei for a trial marriage?

49
00:01:51,530 --> 00:01:52,229
This...

50
00:01:52,229 --> 00:01:53,530
It was my daughter's narrow-mindedness,

51
00:01:53,530 --> 00:01:54,600
using this to humiliate Shen.

52
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:56,759
You just said your family bought the old and weak of the Shen family

53
00:01:56,759 --> 00:01:58,000
out of kindness.

54
00:02:00,730 --> 00:02:01,600
Enough.

55
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:04,730
I can't be bothered with the messy accounts between you.

56
00:02:04,830 --> 00:02:07,360
Lu Jingxing, marry them both.

57
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,500
The Grand Tutor's daughter as your primary wife,

58
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:11,300
and Shen Lvyi as your concubine.

59
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:13,030
Thank you, Your Majesty.

60
00:02:29,460 --> 00:02:30,260
Shen Lvyi,

61
00:02:30,930 --> 00:02:33,030
from now on I am the primary wife and you are the concubine.

62
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:35,260
You are destined to be beneath me for the rest of your life.

63
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,460
Your life and fortune

64
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:39,100
are all in my hands, the General's wife.

65
00:02:40,829 --> 00:02:43,260
No matter how scheming Shen Lvyi is,

66
00:02:43,630 --> 00:02:45,630
the one formally married by General Weibei

67
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:47,500
is still my daughter.

68
00:02:49,060 --> 00:02:52,230
Men always have a moment of novelty.

69
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:55,460
It's all the same after sleeping with her for a while.

70
00:02:55,460 --> 00:02:57,329
Only you, the primary wife,

71
00:02:57,329 --> 00:02:59,190
she must respect you while alive,

72
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,860
and be buried with you after death.

73
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,460
You are right, Mother.

74
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:06,560
I will be in charge of the General's backyard from now on.

75
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,960
I have plenty of time to deal with Shen Lvyi.

76
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,030
By the way,

77
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:11,930
is the matter I ordered settled?

78
00:03:11,930 --> 00:03:12,900
It's settled.

79
00:03:12,900 --> 00:03:15,660
I guarantee that today the Shen family won't even have a single wedding dress,

80
00:03:15,660 --> 00:03:17,500
let alone a piece of red cloth.

81
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:25,230
You are getting married today,

82
00:03:25,430 --> 00:03:27,960
but this wedding dress is ruined like this...

83
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,960
Mother, I don't care about this.

84
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:32,660
You have endured humiliation

85
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:33,990
all for the Shen family,

86
00:03:34,130 --> 00:03:35,630
but you also have Lu Jingxing in your heart.

87
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:36,700
I can see it.

88
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:37,900
God has eyes.

89
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:39,260
He came back to save you.

90
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,060
You finally have a happy ending,

91
00:03:41,060 --> 00:03:43,960
but I couldn't even save a wedding dress for you.

92
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:48,230
The Shen family's grievance has not been cleared.

93
00:03:48,230 --> 00:03:50,829
This marriage is just a part of my plan.

94
00:03:50,829 --> 00:03:52,230
Don't take it seriously.

95
00:03:52,460 --> 00:03:54,990
After all, it's a once-in-a-lifetime thing.

96
00:03:58,430 --> 00:04:00,230
My lady, I'm here for you.

97
00:04:03,460 --> 00:04:04,600
This fool.

98
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:07,030
He knows I hide many things from him,

99
00:04:07,660 --> 00:04:08,990
yet he is still so happy.

100
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,860
Brother-in-law!

101
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:14,430
Take it.

102
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:16,760
Wedding money from your brother-in-law.

103
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:22,360
Brother-in-law is so generous.

104
00:04:24,130 --> 00:04:25,800
I don't have a wedding dress to wear.

105
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,530
Can I just go with you like this?

106
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,260
Even if you wear a rag,

107
00:04:29,260 --> 00:04:30,590
you are still stunning.

108
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:32,530
But on this big day,

109
00:04:32,930 --> 00:04:34,659
you can be even more beautiful.

110
00:04:38,659 --> 00:04:39,500
Bring them in!

111
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:49,730
General, there are over a hundred more that can't fit in. What should we do?

112
00:04:49,730 --> 00:04:50,500
Leave them outside.

113
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:52,860
We will take them to the General's Manor later.

114
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:53,659
This...

115
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:56,100
This is the dowry I prepared for Luyi.

116
00:04:56,630 --> 00:04:57,400
When our house was raided,

117
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:59,200
weren't all these confiscated?

118
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:04,300
Lu Jingxing, did you rob the Imperial Household Department?

119
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:05,330
I didn't rob them.

120
00:05:05,330 --> 00:05:06,200
Didn't you say

121
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,330
I couldn't be arrogant?

122
00:05:07,330 --> 00:05:08,130
I'm obedient.

123
00:05:08,130 --> 00:05:10,330
I traded the treasures His Majesty gave me for them.

124
00:05:10,330 --> 00:05:12,130
Here are all the account books of the General's Manor.

125
00:05:12,130 --> 00:05:13,800
The keys to the storehouse are all yours.

126
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:16,260
Everything I earned is your betrothal gift.

127
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:19,760
I don't care about this.

128
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:23,990
To reunite with you in this life

129
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:25,260
and marry you,

130
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:27,700
even if we are only husband and wife for a few days,

131
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:28,730
I am satisfied.

132
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:36,230
The dowry you prepared for the eldest lady is so complete, Madam.

133
00:05:36,230 --> 00:05:37,830
I'm starting to prepare now,

134
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:40,300
so I won't be in a rush when he tells me his feelings.

135
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:43,360
Our eldest lady has the character and looks of a fairy.

136
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:46,260
She is good enough to marry a royal noble.

137
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:55,900
Don't listen to them.

138
00:05:56,300 --> 00:05:57,630
I don't care about this.

139
00:05:57,830 --> 00:06:00,500
The person I want to marry is you.

140
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,600
Luyi.

141
00:06:07,060 --> 00:06:08,060
No matter what you are looking for,

142
00:06:08,060 --> 00:06:09,260
or what you are planning,

143
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:10,960
no matter if you were sincere to me before,

144
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,160
I don't care anymore.

145
00:06:12,530 --> 00:06:13,830
I just want you.

146
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:16,730
This moment is enough for Lu Jingxing in this life.
